replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:09:28.000Z","msg":"唔係廣告<br />\n係am730編輯用心設計<br />\n好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be2bec3eae06980d010fe5887b635bd3fe98395","tid":1244541,"uid":156130,"like":189,"dislike":2,"score":187,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"擺明頭版標題"},{"pid":"a8d7a31bc35e7dcdbb4002a27ba5c5cc4abb5279","tid":1244541,"uid":62247,"like":170,"dislike":1,"score":169,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:10:09.000Z","msg":"佢自己內文黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c17e5c6befac110f8b28337c259df59b91d174","tid":1244541,"uid":241171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5740ec6b31b422cc51919694a1c54f602427f365","tid":1244541,"uid":21002,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:10:47.000Z","msg":"個波又交番比卡超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c83709112b387ff7d7f7690dc1801192edb010","tid":1244541,"uid":259244,"like":262,"dislike":1,"score":261,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:10:53.000Z","msg":"唔似係廣告<br />\n但排版嗰個將張圖放到咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4766d7b8129076343c83ef536793e155a17ccc","tid":1244541,"uid":49546,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:11:14.000Z","msg":"難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56be51771cdb16e77508ac4a256ccc758f131c7b","tid":1244541,"uid":172244,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"7cb9397a1099cd7d9eeb4d41c1bd19479a2cb0e2","tid":1244541,"uid":182281,"like":399,"dislike":0,"score":399,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"唔係廣告黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"比佢fake左 仲以為有人落廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654436dc82296c5774ffd8ec9566dc0b0aa5cee0","tid":1244541,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:15:22.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56217718928584a445e5bd62613eeaa681e843b3","tid":1244541,"uid":172244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d65189c35a2c2a81cb5a843391d9ebb50f1a5a","tid":1244541,"uid":82917,"like":310,"dislike":1,"score":309,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"朵蓮花真係好撚濕鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faf50326fbdbb978602524ca3a3da632bd49e86","tid":1244541,"uid":123848,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"出黎幫林鄭轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1300f50417dce76fcecbe528466792db7a9b9237","tid":1244541,"uid":172244,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46d65189c35a2c2a81cb5a843391d9ebb50f1a5a","tid":1244541,"uid":82917,"like":310,"dislike":1,"score":309,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"朵蓮花真係好撚濕鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1664afbbb30ee0a4690a37c8d6f795baa90429f","tid":1244541,"uid":140538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有得做，唔落頭板落入面都好"},{"pid":"3e0184b9828527dd61019617ba22e32363349a9e","tid":1244541,"uid":156936,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:13:13.000Z","msg":"【請為621廣泛報料，聽朝七點，政總集合】<br />\n立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府警察勢力分報圖，持續收料，一直更新。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5rtOBOy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5rtOBOy.jpg&h=eae4919c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歡迎加入討論: <strong>圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1</a><br />\n<strong>更多細節請用追故模式</strong><br />\n===============================<br />\n夢見好多人想開放日遊覽禮賓府。<br />\n但聽聞條斜路好危險，驚人多出現意外。<br />\n為安全著想，出席任何活動前，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有義務了解該地環境</span>，<br />\n希望各位唔好一知半解的情況下跟隨人流，造成危險。<br />\n===============================<br />\n禮賓府高空、地則及2018香港地圖懶人包<br />\n===============================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6aA1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6aA1c0.jpg&h=0cd9b552&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTyu5EG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTyu5EG.jpg&h=9be2896f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/20/CalifZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F20%2FCalifZ.jpeg&h=dfe01eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禮賓府交通路線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZoOuRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZoOuRy.jpg&h=6ca9e50d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v6z9Rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v6z9Rz.jpg&h=7291e991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n====================<br />\n禮賓府建議地鐵步行路線<br />\n====================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUqEBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUqEBwz.jpg&h=f978913f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n禮賓府地下通道新聞<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceZBDKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceZBDKW.jpg&h=7ac3a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主現時收集以下的資料及圖片，作學術研究之用 :<br />\n<del>1. 禮賓府正確的出入口和閘門總數(己達成)</del><br />\n<del>2. 禮賓府旁舊樓梯及非行車小徑等Google Map無法標示之通道(己達成)</del><br />\n3. 急救站、飲水機、洗手間或可設立急救站空地等休息位置<br />\n4. 立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府野生犬隻出沒或聚居地點 (可以Google map mark比我最好)<br />\n<del>5. 由蘭桂坊或香港動植物公園前往的最佳路線(己達成)</del><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[同我推晒佢] 力抗膠post 621行動討論整合</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242813/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242813/page/1</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">催淚彈、胡椒噴霧</span></span></strong><br />\n發夢夢到幾個德國朋友教我點處理催淚彈 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1218344/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1218344/page/1</a><br />\n[Gear撚] 催淚彈對防指南 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1</a><br />\n［學術］中咗催淚彈同胡椒噴霧解決方法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1</a><br />\n[廣傳][長文]長期革命，每個人都要準備對抗催淚彈/胡椒噴磅必須用品 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">裝備</span></span></strong><br />\n&lt;抗爭手冊&gt; <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2</a><br />\n振興香港消費！全城戶外運動裝備及須知 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1</a><br />\n知己知彼 百戰百勝圖解香港警察裝備 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1</a><br />\n最近有個新喪屍GAME IDEA <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1</a><br />\n[突發] 621 雙方陣營裝備分析 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1</a><br />\n[魔防的重要性］所有人都要有足夠魔防 N95同泳鏡係最低要求 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1</a><br />\n星期五嘅野餐行動 請現在立即做兩樣野 購買裝備 同 加強文宣 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241812/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241812/page/1</a><br />\n緊急！邊度可以買魔防裝 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242751/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242751/page/1</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">盾牌</span></span></strong><br />\n[歷史台][積極備盾] 盾牌陣不是亂擺一通的 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241049/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241049/page/1</a><br />\n廉價盾牌材料 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1200677/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1200677/page/1</a><br />\n對付警犬最強盾牌buff <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216654/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216654/page/1</a><br />\n盾牌警棍頭盔：反政府示威者裝備不輸警察 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240310/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240310/page/1</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鐵馬</span></span></strong><br />\n鐵馬一定要放最前！鐵馬一定要有流動性！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1238720/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1238720/page/1</a><br />\n[人人都要識] 倒三角扎鐵馬 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240447/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240447/page/1</a><br />\n鐵馬最新安置法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">IT</span></span></strong><br />\n[正式上架] 手機抗警犬 用相機Scan數字即出黑警資料 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241300/page/1</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">雞蛋、漆彈、洗潔精</span></span></strong><br />\n漆彈大作戰遊戲攻略 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216185/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216185/page/1</a><br />\n勇武 掉雞蛋好撚on9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242300/page/1</a> <br />\n621美食節之如何不令雞蛋發臭 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242159/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242159/page/1</a><br />\n咪撚再講用油/洗潔精/波子 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241029/page/1</a><br />\n記得準備定大量黑色噴漆！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202312/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202312/page/1</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">戰術/宏觀部署 </span></span></strong><br />\n拋磚引玉，大家一齊討論下前線戰術有咩要改善 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1226009/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1226009/page/1</a><br />\n[定向討論集中地］21/6嘅去向太多講法，混亂嘅你入一入黎 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242563/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242563/page/1</a><br />\n621部署建議，入嚟討論，搵到方向好重要。 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241497/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241497/page/1</a><br />\n前線有d感想想同香港人講 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1218876/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1218876/page/1</a><br />\n&lt;&lt;夢見嚟緊最大型野餐係621明日大嶼開會日&gt;&gt; <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1234173/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1234173/page/1</a><br />\n［純學術討論］漫談「間接路線」軍事理論 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242381/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242381/page/1</a><br />\n高Lv戰士刷副本心得 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241700/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241700/page/1</a><br />\n反送中遊行今日再起！3種戰術隨你選 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1229215/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1229215/page/1</a><br />\n共產黨起家戰術就係：敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1236578/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1236578/page/1</a><br />\n野餐中期檢討 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1214271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1214271/page/1</a><br />\n[為621做好準備] 612檢討大會正式開始討論！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240552/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240552/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不合作運動</span></span></strong><br />\n暴徒最新交通癱瘓計劃整合 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1215053/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1215053/page/1</a><br />\n塞地鐵啦 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1213061/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1213061/page/1</a><br />\n聽日地鐵，三隧，青馬大橋!!!!!!! <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1210799/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1210799/page/1</a><br />\n[齊心就會成功] 621和理非 不合作運動提案 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240871/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240871/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府全部都相當有歷史價值，係一家大細親子好去處，大家記得要遵守秩序，<span style=\"color: red;\">去之前記得做足功課</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時無開放千奇唔好去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3516ec3a3a177589307e0b2d513cf1da5b8f0c10","tid":1244541,"uid":172244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebc2a4f538fbc9f82cb4b30a1eaf5d558c768fa","tid":1244541,"uid":193919,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"個「認同請分享」簡直係畫龍點睛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5b40ed495e44161db7622434d241cdfcc6e5f3","tid":1244541,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:14:52.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f558091e81521dff0eb0ea706e52cd0afcdd61","tid":1244541,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:16:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a73fb7d108c53ed8f61b0f42f06d05e2fe3ec24","tid":1244541,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2007b8705e90f3458e4f2e0f8a6ac9658d2d8dcd","tid":1244541,"uid":187437,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/am730hk/videos/327345734821893/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fam730hk%2Fvideos%2F327345734821893%2F&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=9207055b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.faceb